    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi Dei eterni, anno ab eius
                        nativitate millesimo centesimo septuagesimo quinto, pridie kalendarum
                        februarii, indictione octava. Manifesti sumus nos <persName><name
                                ref="Balduinus">Baldinus</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Rainerius">Rainerius</name></persName> germani quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Confrater">Confratris</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Cederna"/></persName> uxor suprascripti Baldini
                        et <persName><name ref="Sirica">Sirica</name></persName> uxor suprascripti
                        Rainerii (…) ubi interfuit notitia <persName key="#Judge"><name
                                ref="Zoccolus">Zocoli</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs> (…) per hanc cartulam vendimus et tradimus
                        tibi <persName><name ref="Montanus">Montanino</name></persName>, rectori
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3206" key="#Hospitals"><rs
                                key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs> de <placeName key="#Hospitals"
                                ref="#places/3207">Altopasso</placeName></orgName>, videlicet omnes
                        terra cultas et incultas, donicatas et massaritias atque agrestes quas
                        habemus et aliquo modo nobis pertinent in loco et finibus <placeName
                            ref="#places/3210">Putei</placeName> et <placeName ref="#places/3231"
                            >Lingiani</placeName> et <placeName ref="#places/63">Sancte Marie ad
                            Montem</placeName>, quas tenent <persName><name ref="Hugolinus"
                                >Ugolinus</name></persName> et filii eius massarii et
                                <persName><name ref="Georgius">Georgiolus</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Grillus"/></persName> item massarii et
                                <persName><name ref="Lingianus">Lingianus</name></persName>
                        massarius et filii <persName><name ref="Petrus/Andreas">Petri
                            Andree</name></persName> similiter massarii et quas tenet *** de Sancta
                        Maria ad Montem et quas tenet <persName><name ref="Aldebrandus"
                                >Aldebrandinus</name></persName> passarecius et quas tenet
                                <persName><name ref="Bellonatus">Bellonatus</name></persName> seu tu
                        qui supra Montaninus pro ipso hospitali tenes vel aliquis pro ipso hospitali
                        tenet vel quas aliqua alia persona in predictis locis et finibus de nostris
                        terris et possesionibus aliquo modo habet seu tenet, et omne ius et actionem
                        nobis exinde aliquo modo pertinentia. (…) <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: libram
                        decem et septem bonorum denariorum lucensium. (…) <foreign>Pena</foreign>:
                        in duplum (…) et insuper argenti optimi libras quatuor. (…) Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/464">Piscie maiori</placeName> ad predicti iugales hanc
                        cartulam fieri rogaverunt. (…) <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Raginulfus">Rainulfus</name></persName> filius <persName><name
                                ref="Rainerius">Rainerii</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Gherardus">Girardinus</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Heinricus">Arigetti</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Raginaldus"
                            >Rainaldinus</name></persName> filius <persName><name ref="Wido"
                                >Guidi</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Benettus">Benettus</name></persName> quondam *** et
                                <persName><name ref="Wilielmus">Guilielmus</name></persName> medicus
                        rogati <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs> interfuerunt. (S) <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Aldricus">Aldricus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domni imperatoris post traditam complevi et
                        dedi. </ab>
